 related to restructuring actions designed", "bbox": [177.2, 964.6, 1094.3, 981.3]}, {"text": "to better align resources with growth opportunities and to reduce costs as a result of current and anticipated market conditions. See Note", "bbox": [177.2, 985.5, 1094.2, 1002.1]}, {"text": "14 in the Financial Statements for more information.", "bbox": [177.2, 1006.3, 527.6, 1023.0]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [143.8, 1039.7, 163.2, 1056.3]}, {"text": "Includes costs of $43.5 million ($27.7 million after tax, or $0.17 per diluted share) related to various restructuring activities designed to", "bbox": [177.2, 1039.7, 1094.2, 1056.3]}, {"text": "execute on our cost productivity initiatives and to advance our globalization strategy. See Note 14 in the Financial Statements for more", "bbox": [177.2, 1060.5, 1094.2, 1077.2]}, {"text": "information.", "bbox": [177.2, 1081.3, 260.1, 1098.0]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [143.8, 1114.7, 162.3, 1131.4]}, {"text": "Includes a gain on sale of our 50 percent interest in Rockwell Scientific Company LLC (RSC) of $19.9 million ($12.0 million after tax,", "bbox": [177.2, 1114.7, 1094.2, 1131.4]}, {"text": "or $0.07 per diluted share).", "bbox": [177.2, 1135.5, 357.5, 1152.2]}, {"text": "(d)", "bbox": [143.8, 1168.9, 163.2, 1185.5]}, {"text": "Effective September 30, 2006, we adopted Financial Accounting Standards Board (FASB) Interpretation No. 47, Accounting for", "bbox": [177.2, 1168.7, 1094.3, 1185.5]}, {"text": "Conditional Asset Retirement Obligations (FIN 47), which clarifies the guidance included in Statement of Financial Accounting", "bbox": [177.2, 1189.5, 1094.2, 1206.4]}, {"text": "Standards (SFAS) No. 143, Accounting for Asset Retirement Obligations (SFAS 143). The application of FIN 47 resulted in a charge of", "bbox": [177.2, 1210.4, 1094.2, 1227.2]}, {"text": "$28.6 million ($17.7 million after tax, or $0.10 per diluted share) in 2006.", "bbox": [177.2, 1231.4, 668.4, 1248.1]}, {"text": "15", "bbox": [608.6, 1478.3, 629.4, 149